"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-06-26-convicted-child-rapist-set-represent-netherlands-olympics-21111467\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Netherlands have selected Steven van de Velde, a convicted child rapist, on their volleyball team for theOlympicsthissummer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999928350007, \"rank\": 7.056107483811528e-09, \"text\": \"The Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999765541217226, \"rank\": 2.344642785523367e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was jailed for four years in March 2016for raping a 12-year-old British girl in Milton Keynes in 2014.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.996717712576151, \"rank\": 0.0032499914412437436, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.629029172419014e-28, \"text\": \"Milton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Milton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After being sentenced, Judge Francis Sheridan told Van de Velde: 'Prior to coming to this country you were training as a potential Olympian.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"score\": 0.9999989432586643, \"rank\": 1.0413029898837339e-06, \"text\": \"Francis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope_Francis\"}, {\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9479269017907098, \"rank\": 0.05492288358848161, \"text\": \"Sheridan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheridan_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996125553, \"rank\": 3.8764732881529853e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your hopes of representing your country now lie as a shattered dream.'\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was released in 2017 after serving only 12 months in prison in the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999033389078, \"rank\": 6.749336836727e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde then resumed his career in beach volleyball and will represent the Netherlands alongside his 23-year-old partner Matthew Immers at the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999033389078, \"rank\": 6.749336836727e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999929864316, \"rank\": 7.013350354408791e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch Volleyball Federation (Nevobo) has supported Van de Velde's inclusion at the Games this summer.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6631978902961215, \"rank\": 0.5076997515140748, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"score\": 0.9999999987030606, \"rank\": 1.29610313214265e-09, \"text\": \"Volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We know Steven's history.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before he expressed his desire to return to beach volleyball at the time, we spoke extensively with him but also with NOC*NSF and the international volleyball federation FIVB, among others,' said Michel Everaert, general director at Nevobo.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NOC*NSF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He was convicted at the time according to English law and he has served his sentence.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From then on, we have been in constant contact with Steven, who has now been fully reintegrated into the Dutch volleyball community.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6631978902961215, \"rank\": 0.5076997515140748, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is proving to be an exemplary professional and human being and there has been no reason to doubt him since his return.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We fully support him and his participation in Paris, which he and Matthew have earned.'\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999929864316, \"rank\": 7.013350354408791e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch Olympic Committee (NOC) said in a statement: 'After his release, Van de Velde sought and received professional counselling.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.22340355237109e-29, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 0.9999993653620745, \"rank\": 6.346384690015426e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He demonstrated to those around him - privately and professionally - self-insight and reflection.'\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement provided by the NOC, Van de Velde said: 'In 2016 and afterwards, several Dutch media also paid attention to the story.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1787, \"end\": 1790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 0.9999993653620745, \"rank\": 6.346384690015426e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6631978902961215, \"rank\": 0.5076997515140748, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand that in the run-up to the biggest sporting event in the world, this can attract the attention of international media.'\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the International Olympic Committee (IOC), which governs the Olympics, has said it will not intervene.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The nomination of individual team members, following qualification on the field of play, is the sole responsibility of each respective National Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.497304320677984e-12, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, we would refer to the Dutch NOC for any further information,' a statement read.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6631978902961215, \"rank\": 0.5076997515140748, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 0.9999993653620745, \"rank\": 6.346384690015426e-07, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toThe Times, the British Olympic Association has 'grave concerns' overthe Netherlands' decision.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2478, \"end\": 2489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999033389078, \"rank\": 6.749336836727e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde, who was 19 at the time of the rape, contacted the 12-year-old victim on Facebook before travelling from the Netherlands to the UK in order to meet.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999033389078, \"rank\": 6.749336836727e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 2643, \"end\": 2645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999945081686572, \"rank\": 5.480005335947567e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde pleaded guilty to three counts of rape and wept in court after learning about the schoolgirl's subsequent self-harm and overdose.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His own defence lawyer, Linda Strudwick, said: 'He's lost a stellar sporting career and he's being branded a rapist.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\", \"score\": 0.5994193556614009, \"rank\": 0.5317141721582717, \"text\": \"Linda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_McCartney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Holland the term means violent sexual assault without consent.\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9995173986849787, \"rank\": 0.0004826875090350084, \"text\": \"Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The headlines say it all - 'a sex monster.'\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's plainly a career end for him.'\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after his release in 2017, Van de Velde said: 'I do want to correct all nonsense which has been written about me when I was locked up.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not read anything of it, on purpose.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I understand that it was quite bad, that I have been branded as a sex monster, as a paedophile.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That I am not, really not.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Everyone can have an opinion about me, but it is only fair if they also know my side of the story.'\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with Dutch media a year later, he said: 'I cannot reverse it, so I will have to bear the consequences.\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3513, \"end\": 3518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.6631978902961215, \"rank\": 0.5076997515140748, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been the biggest mistake of my life.'\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \